{"tid":1599853,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】【101支線任】漫天心聲布","createTime":"2019-09-28T08:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T12:24:29.000Z","uid":293887,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e647a2c0f3e51475accde9319a1288265f8426c","tid":1599853,"uid":293887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"人地國慶就歡歡樂樂，好自豪咁掛國旗去慶祝，Well，我係唔會阻止你咁大愛掛枝核突紅色野係屋企既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地要把心聲突破新高度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n今次！認真！<span style=\"color: gold;\">召集大家101搵個地方掛上banner</span> ，要有人望到嫁！<br />\n學校、商場、天橋、天台，最簡單就係自己屋企既窗外，想挑戰難度既可以上下山咁，有金既可以租返架直升機威威子先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n喇，驚大家唔記得，再提提各位<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港係法治社會</span>黎嫁麻(應該係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n寫乜唔洗教啦，落樓下連農牆睇下<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>目的：</ins></strong><br />\n－ 把<span style=\"color: red;\">我地對民主既饑渴射出國際、射到外太空</span> <br />\n－ 用香港人既意志，<span style=\"color: red;\">粉飾城市</span><br />\n－ 鼓勵同路人<br />\n－ 個個都容易參與<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>心聲布做法：</ins></strong> <br />\n買一幅布 加顏料 ／marker / 膠紙 自由發揮<br />\n兩條索帶索佢LM，完～<br />\n掛完驚柒左既最好自己落街睇返<br />\n如果佢飄黎飄去既可以個底加重少少<br />\nbtw溫提：布料店好多都係星期日同公眾假期唔開，<span style=\"color: red;\">呢兩日好買定啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tNgSkDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtNgSkDK.jpg&h=820e5808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家101出發前掛起佢 <br />\n無論和理非又好勇武又好都可以一齊參與<br />\n出黎行街見到都精力充沛呀<br />\n<br />\n交流／交相／交..... 咩都好，呢到：<a href=\"http://t.me/hihihihi123454321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhihihihi123454321&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=de299e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/hihihihi123454321</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個活動可唔可以加入去日程表上面呀??<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好期待呢日香港滿天民意，鼓勵加油既心聲 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0ee1cd0b6b4d8db2a462382ba50ac3cddd343313","tid":1599853,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"5d94fa2e47fea2c47c96234ff1bcdd35fd088046","tid":1599853,"uid":310614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"018997bbc3cc2950aa31760fcb7d3e34cf007f20","tid":1599853,"uid":293887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"自推下先"},{"pid":"48f4826be19d70b3664d98b608525f069daf2deb","tid":1599853,"uid":56311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"<strong>推Post及借位宣傳下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新產品:連登書籤</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u21CrB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu21CrB4.jpg&h=9f2e17b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">link:<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/IRrY8V1N/反送中lihkg-portal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2FIRrY8V1N%2F%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%ADlihkg-portal&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=1ad63b95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/IRrY8V1N/反送中lihkg-portal</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">八大</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">分</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">類</span><span style=\